340
00:28:32,134 --> 00:28:33,834
Respeitabilidade?

341
00:28:34,634 --> 00:28:37,542
Nada mal.
Estou impressionada.

342
00:28:38,967 --> 00:28:40,426
Ao trabalho, queridas!

343
00:28:40,427 --> 00:28:43,888
